{"tid":100424,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我發覺你地呢班毒撚真係好撚核突","createTime":"2017-01-30T04:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T13:42:55.000Z","uid":31374,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa137cb15122877b27d97600b4dcf3b82a66a627","tid":100424,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"成日浪費時間睇埋哂D無謂野<br />\n睇完邊套邊套野就懶係有感觸咁又話要點又話要點<br />\n又係度講入面Ｄ對白，人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n以為自己係動漫男主？<br />\n好心你地就照下塊鏡睇下你地似D乜<br />\n油頭粉面口氣臭唔在講，雙目無光成隻彊屍咁先得人驚呀嘛<br />\n溝唔到女就話自己只係討厭三次元，係度玩Gal game當自己情聖<br />\n我就估你地係現實連同人對望都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你地只係逃避緊現實，柒夠就醒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我今日會黎屌醒你地，其實都係因為呢個係命運石之門既選擇。"},{"pid":"3e3c39e2240d07dcd123269692b77594a2c13da8","tid":100424,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<br />\nEl psy congroo"},{"pid":"6cb3008e8b5840a96a09e22e949ef7c464f48edc","tid":100424,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好波<br />\nEl psy congroo</blockquote><br />\n一齊屌醒班廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57af8c0abd6280697e95a033a3de3797d3f277d2","tid":100424,"uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:24:39.000Z","msg":"命運石之門好睇乎？"},{"pid":"1abc0c5d62261cb0c57ec9ea6c223704dadbbb52","tid":100424,"uid":71487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:25:45.000Z","msg":"赤口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁快開鳩人年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b7c171cd43bd815eabda2d5005c2f95d18271e","tid":100424,"uid":21964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"好想樓主瘋狂屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370285b0107ff5dc